                        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-warm-gray">
                            <p>13 science-backed ingredients across three products: a morning powder blend (6 ingredients), morning softgels (4 ingredients), and evening capsules (3 ingredients). Every ingredient is dosed at clinical trial levels &mdash; no hidden doses, no hidden amounts.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

